snippet.title: Mowgli Trailer | Roshan Kanakala | Bandi Saroj Kumar | Sandeep Raj | Sakkshi | TG Vishwa Prasad
snippet.description:
Mowgli 2025 will arrive in cinemas on December 12th, 2025.

Mowgli is an upcoming 2025 unique romantic action drama set deep within a forest backdrop. Directed by National Award-winning filmmaker Sandeep Raj (Colour Photo), Produced by TG Vishwa Prasad and Krithi Prasad under People Media Factory Banner.The film has cinematography by Rama Maruthi M, while Kaala Bhairava scores the music. The work is co-written by Rama Maruthi M and Radhakrishna Reddy The technical team also includes Peekay as editor, Kiran Mamidi as art director, and Natraj Madigonda choreographing the action sequences.

snippet.title: Pawan Singh New Song | Dhamaka | Trishakar Madhu | Power Star | New Bhojpuri Song | Bhojpuri Gana
snippet.description:
इलाका रहे केहुवो के जान "धमाका" हमरे होई |
पावरस्टार पवन सिंह ज़बरदस्त धमाका करने आ गए हैं! दमदार अंदाज़, ताबड़तोड़ एनर्जी और पूरी मस्ती से भरपूर उनका नया धमाकेदार गाना दर्शकों का दिल जीतने वाला है। तैयार हो जाइए पवन सिंह के इस नए धमाके का मज़ा लेने के लिए।

Subscribe to our channel for more Bhojpuri Songs:
https://youtube.com/c/SaregamaHumBhojpuri

Credits:-

Singer - Pawan Singh & Shilpi Raj
Featuring -   Pawan Singh & Trishakar Madhu 
Music & Composer - Shubham Raj ( SBR)
Lyrics - Prince Shaan Dubey 
Choreographer -Sunny Sonkar
Director - Goldi Jaiswal 
Dop - Vazeer
Editor : Narendra Jaiswal
Di Studio - Arts for Production 
Colorist - Tapasvi Asija 
Confirming - Kunal Singh

Lyrics:-

Dhamaka 
F-गुंडागर्दी चली न 
   दाल राउर गली न
 लेके पिस्तौल खुद के
  बुझी बाहुबली न् |
M-हम रख देनी जेकरा पे हाथ उ पाक्का हमरे होई
   इलाका रहे केहुवो के जान धमाका हमरे होई

अंतरा 1
F- नाच देखे आइल बानी माजा ली नाच के
   पड़अतानी चक्कर मे काहे तीन पांच के
M- लाख दुलाख आखिर केतना
    माल तु बताव चाही जेतना 
  जवन शहर से करबे तु पार उ नाका हमरे होई
इलाका रहे....

अंतरा 2
F-नोट के जादा न गर्मी देखाई 
   राजाबाबु होने नजर हटाई
M-आ गईल चीज जे पसंद हो 
    छोड़े न ओकरा पवन हो
   जवना बल पे उडेले रंगदार उ काटा हमरे होई
  इलाका रहे.....

💔 “Aji Rati Gale Pahi Jaliba Mo Jui” is a heart-touching Odia sad song that reflects the pain of separation, unspoken feelings, and emotional heartbreak sang by Humane Sagar. The soulful voice and emotional lyrics beautifully bring out the depth of love that has been lost, making this track relatable for anyone who has experienced sadness in love.The song captures the journey of someone who still cherishes their beloved (Jui – meaning the light of life) even after distance and destiny have created a painful gap. Its melody, music arrangement, and emotional expression make it a powerful sad song that stays with listeners long after it ends.
